sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as NguoiDung
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant TaskSvc as TaskService
participant Queue as RabbitMQ
participant Worker as TaskFromFileWorker

Note over User,Worker: Chặng 2 - Tạo task từ file chat + ngoại lệ
User->>Client: Tạo task từ file chat
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/tasks/from-chat-file
Gateway->>TaskSvc: Forward
TaskSvc->>Queue: Enqueue job
TaskSvc-->>Client: 202 accepted
Queue->>Worker: Consume job xử lý nền
alt Job thành công
  Worker-->>Client: Trạng thái hoàn tất
else Retry thất bại
  Worker-->>Client: Cảnh báo chờ xử lý lại
end
